content:
The hydra user enumeration attempt took too long and was terminated.

Since brute forcing usernames with large lists on this SSH server is too slow or limited, I will switch strategy.

Next, I will run a UDP scan on the top 100 ports instead of only 50, hoping for other services that might be useful for initial access.

Command: nmap -sU --top-ports 100 -Pn -oN udp_top100_scan.txt 172.10.0.3

If interesting UDP services are found, I will target those for further enumeration.
